    }), "At the end of the service, the announcement was made for new members  to either join the  Wednesday or the Thursday Bible study group. I decided to join the Thursday group and needless to say that I was terribly disappointed when I did not see the Sunday crowd on Thursday and the music was \u2018one kind\u2019. However the fellowship was rich and people smiled genuinely. I sat besides a Sister who I later knew to be Yinka Ajomale. She prayed and worshipped as if she was listening to a different kind of music than what I was hearing.", /*#__PURE__*/React.createElement("br", {
