m, we served together at one time or the other for which I am most grateful to;<br/>The Roll Call:<br/>Brother Lawal Lanipekun Reeves, Brothers Tenu, Okiki, Morgan, Bola Adedimeji, Kehinde Olatoye, Muyiwa Ajakaiye, Ayo Ogunremi, Sola Ajibulu, etc<br/>Sisters Ronke Adebayo, Sola Ajiboso, Nike Adesogan, Bola Olusesi, Funmi Olukoju, Tundun Fasina, Dayo, Femi, etc.<br/>SCM made UI worth attending for me.<br/>I will also want to state that we demonstrated the sincere love of God amongst us. The way we visit and care for one another almost attracted even Executive Members of other fellowships to join us.<br/>I will want to specially appreciate our able Presidents between 87-91;
