              <br/>In my final year,  when I had less work load ( we all know Pharmacy wahala)  My able room mate,  friend,  confidant and sister was on my neck. The able Sister Bukky.  I love songs and sing a lot,  she encouraged me and make sure I joined the choir.  Then one day the Drama leader (cant remember who again)  also picked me up on discovering the talents I had been hiding .
